headline: Principal® Recognized as "Best Place to Work for Disability Inclusion"
summary: DES MOINES, Iowa, July 15, 2025--Principal Financial Group® was named to the list of the "Best Places to Work for Disability Inclusion" after earning a top score of 100 on a scale of zero to 100 on the 2025 Disability Equality Index®, the world’s most comprehensive benchmarking tool for companies to measure workplace disability inclusion.
